    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>This structure is used by the <see cref="GetResourceTiling" />     method.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/cd3dx12-tile-shape">CD3DX12_TILE_SHAPE</seealso>
